video.title: Greenhouse Academy
video.synopsis: When teen siblings Hayley and Alex enter an elite boarding school, they find rivalry, romance and a mystery related to the recent loss of their mom.

episodes.synopsis: Eight months after the sudden loss of his astronaut mom, Alex undergoes rigorous entrance testing to attend the same leadership high school she did.
episodes.title: Pilot

episodes.synopsis: For their first challenge, the Eagles and Ravens compete to solve a riddle. To be accepted by his team, Alex distances himself from his older sister.
episodes.title: The Opening Challenge

episodes.synopsis: The Eagles pressure Alex to help them get revenge against the Ravens. FBI agents look for a weapon lost near campus and suspect a student took it.
episodes.title: Breaking and Entering

episodes.synopsis: Brooke spots boyfriend Daniel doing something suspicious on the beach. Jackie gets to know Max's sweet side when he helps her with an assignment.
episodes.title: Private Screening

episodes.synopsis: The secret Daniel has been hiding is dramatically unveiled. Chess whiz Max meets his match. Hayley and Leo's friendship takes a sudden turn.
episodes.title: Black Smoke

episodes.synopsis: Hayley gets upset when Leo avoids talking about what happened between them. Max tries to impress his crush, Emma, in gym class.
episodes.title: Captain Material

episodes.synopsis: The Eagles' two candidates for team captain face off in a debate. In class, the students argue over a hypothetical moral dilemma.
episodes.title: Swimming Lessons

episodes.synopsis: Jackie coaches Max in asking Emma out on a date. Jason receives an important but risky mission he must carry out at the satellite launch.
episodes.title: The Outsider

episodes.synopsis: Brooke's investigations lead her to danger and a discovery. When Sophie makes the Eagle boys clean their stinky locker room, a secret is uncovered.
episodes.title: Steph

episodes.synopsis: At the school's Harvest Fair, the Eagles and the Ravens compete to see which team can raise more scholarship money by marketing and selling cupcakes.
episodes.title: Guilt-Free Cupcakes

episodes.synopsis: Ryan's letter reveals a secret she kept from her husband for years. When Emma turns him down, Max takes Jackie instead to the Halloween dance.
episodes.title: Great Scott

episodes.synopsis: Hayley learns who Leo's surprise visitor is. Emma faces consequences for her phone call to NASA. Jealous Daniel's temper explodes at the school dance.
episodes.title: L.D.R.

episodes.synopsis: Flashbacks reveal a discovery that teenage Ryan made at the Greenhouse and an order given shortly before the Athena launch. Brooke is led into a trap.
episodes.title: Escape Mechanism

episodes.synopsis: During a quiz game, know-it-all Aspen grates on Hayley's nerves and Brooke suffers a strange lapse in memory. Max misses Emma and tries calling her.
episodes.title: The Client

episodes.synopsis: When Aspen's jealousy gets the better of her, Leo tells her they need to talk. Judy and Marcus trigger a test quake and get unexpected results.
episodes.title: A Day Off

episodes.synopsis: Under the sea, Hayley experiences something that changes how she thinks about her mom. Believing the world is ending, Parker blurts out a confession.
episodes.title: Meant to Be

episodes.synopsis: Sophie finds herself shunned by all the Eagles -- except for one. Daniel gets a hunch as to who might be influencing Brooke's recent behavior.
episodes.title: Surfing Lessons

episodes.synopsis: After catching his mom in lie, Daniel compares notes with Hayley. Aspen makes a slip that shocks Leo. Jackie is tricked into confessing a past misdeed.
episodes.title: The Workshop

episodes.synopsis: Hayley and Daniel attempt to dehypnotize Brooke. Max and Jackie start to see a common thread behind all the strange events surrounding Emma.
episodes.title: The Spiral

episodes.synopsis: Brooke tells Daniel and Hayley the last things she can remember before being hypnotized. Marcus makes a decision that stuns Louis and infuriates Judy.
episodes.title: More Than a Hunch

episodes.synopsis: Leo awakens in the cave. During dinner with their parents, Brooke and Daniel carry out a plan to get Emma's white knight chess pieces from Jason.
episodes.title: A Born Leader

episodes.synopsis: When Hayley tells her brother and friends the big news, they argue over whether to take action. Max and Jackie are caught trying to contact Emma.
episodes.title: Kyle

episodes.synopsis: While Daniel and Alex stall for time at the basketball game, Hayley sneaks into the cave and Max gets help from an unexpected ally.
episodes.title: Bad Decisions

episodes.synopsis: As time runs out on a bomb designed to destroy the cave and the rest of the Greenhouse, the students in the gym must get past police to make a rescue.
episodes.title: Home

episodes.synopsis: When the Eagles and Ravens start getting too friendly, the headmaster sends them on a grueling two-day hike devised to reignite their competitive fire.
episodes.title: The Hike

episodes.synopsis: The fallout from the hike reverberates inside and outside the school, leading to hard questions -- and a difficult decision.
episodes.title: The Interrogation

episodes.synopsis: Brooke scrambles to keep a secret from Alex during an upheaval at the Greenhouse. Sophie's past choices threaten her current status at the school.
episodes.title: The Perfect Solution

episodes.synopsis: As a sinister plot targeting the school unfolds, Hayley embraces her new lifestyle, annoying Leo, while Brooke argues with Alex about her brother.
episodes.title: Your New Best Friend

episodes.synopsis: A remarkable gift from Ryan boosts the Ravens' flagging spirits. Becca smothers Leo with attention. Brooke makes an impulsive, ill-timed decision.
episodes.title: Old Trophies

episodes.synopsis: Members of the Eagles and Ravens team up on a risky mission to find a valuable chunk of magnetite. A disheartened Brooke looks to make a fresh start.
episodes.title: A Piece of Moon Rock

episodes.synopsis: While the Eagles and Ravens compete in a capture-the-flag challenge, Enzo receives a mysterious offer that's too lucrative for him to question.
episodes.title: The Hidden Flag

episodes.synopsis: Hayley's determination to get to the bottom of an annoying beeping noise unwittingly sets a deadly chain of events into motion.
episodes.title: The Beeps

episodes.synopsis: After an explosion rocks the school, one student hopes for a rescue while another one faces a threat from a mysterious virus.
episodes.title: Rock by Rock

episodes.synopsis: As Hayley considers a risky way to save her classmate, the Eagles and the Ravens have a theory about the mystery virus.
episodes.title: The Quick One

episodes.synopsis: Leo's setback creates tension between Hayley and Daniel. Meanwhile, an FBI investigation results in several major revelations.
episodes.title: A Not Totally Bad Person

episodes.synopsis: Trusted with personal information, Becca and Daniel each battle their true emotions. A schedule change poses a serious problem for a shadowy enemy.
episodes.title: Gummy Bears

episodes.synopsis: The shadowy enemy puts a sinister plan in motion. Later, Sophie investigates questionable news while Daniel debates making a confession.
episodes.title: Cortinarius Orellanus

episodes.synopsis: As the Eagles and the Ravens examine evidence from an attack, a suspicious text from Leo leads them all to a shocking discovery.
episodes.title: Hundred Percent

episodes.synopsis: As Hayley, Daniel and Leo edge closer to learning the truth behind the mystery virus, their real feelings about each other finally come out.
episodes.title: Room 205

episodes.synopsis: Time is ticking as the shadowy figure makes a frightening ultimatum. Can the Eagles and the Ravens intervene in time to save the world?
episodes.title: The Client
